.TH "nvme_init_get_log_device_self_test" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_device_self_test" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_device_self_test \- Initialize passthru command for Device Self-test
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_device_self_test
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_self_test_log *log "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "log" 12
Userspace address of the log payload
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_DEVICE_SELF_TEST.
